data.description: Motivated seller!  Here is your opportunity to own a super cute home in a quiet neighborhood with a big back yard!  Conveniently located within a short drive to the hospital, school and pharmacy as well as several stores and restaurants yet secluded enough for some peace and tranquility in your own back yard.  Fully remodeled by it's previous owners in 2022, it has 2-3 bedrooms, a beautiful modern bathroom, a new kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a handy built-in hallway cupboard and the best part is the tongue and groove ceilings everywhere you look!  There are hand-made sliding barn doors in two of the rooms so that they can have versatile use.  Notice the electric wall fireplaces and several ceiling fans with dimmer switches to circulate the air.  Home has a metal roof for years of protection.  Interior and exterior paint, sheetrock, windows and doors are less than 3 years old.  The current owner has also added a new propane furnace and central air!  If you are looking for a home ready for you to just move right in, come take a look at this one!
